<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<base href="/">
<title>Mangopay Payment Admin</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/bootstrap.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/bootstrap-theme.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/application.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/adduser.css">
<script src="js/jquery-1.12.4.min.js"></script>
<script src="js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container main hidden">
        <div class="row header">
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-xs-12 col-sm-offset-3">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <h1 class="boldi light-blue">Ipefix Payment Solution</h1>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row content">
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-xs-12 border-right">
                <div class="content-left">
                    <h2 class="dark-blue boldi">Ajouter un vendeur</h2>
                    <form action="{{ path_for('newuser') }}" method="post">
                        <input type="hidden" name="{{csrf.keys.name}}" value="{{csrf.name}}">
                        <input type="hidden" name="{{csrf.keys.value}}" value="{{csrf.value}}">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="domain" placeholder="Domaine" pattern="^(http:\/\/www\.|https:\/\/www\.|http:\/\/|https:\/\/)?[a-z0-9]+([\-\.]{1}[a-z0-9]+)*\.[a-z]{2,5}(:[0-9]{1,5})?(\/.*)?$" required><span class="validity"></span>
                            <input type="email" class="form-control" name="email" placeholder="E-mail" required><span class="validity"></span>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="ukey" placeholder="User-id" pattern="[0-9]*" required><span class="validity"></span>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="wkey" placeholder="Wallet-id" pattern="[0-9]*" required><span class="validity"></span>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="bkey" placeholder="Bank-account" pattern="[0-9]*" required><span class="validity"></span>
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default btn-sm btn-block bold">Ajouter</button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-xs-12 border-left">
                <div class="content-right">
                    <p>
                        Inscrivez l'adresse du site internet client 
                        ( exemple : www.the-site.com )
                        devant bénéficier du service, seule les liens 
                        venant de ce domaine seront pris en compte. 
                        L'e-mail servira à notifier votre client. 
                        Créez votre <strong>"Seller"</strong>, pour ce faire: 
                        créez un <strong>"User"</strong>, sa <strong>"Wallet"</strong> et 
                        son <strong>"Bank account"</strong> dans votre 
                        <a href="https://api.mangopay.com/" target="_blank">Dashboard</a> Mangoopay.
                        Inscrivez ici son "user-id", "wallet-id" et "bank-id". 
                        Il est facile de les <strong>"Copier/Coller"</strong> depuis l'interface.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row footer">
            <div class="col-sm-4 col-sm-offset-4">
                <div class="text-center copyr">&copy; Ipefix 2019</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container loader"></div>
    <script src="js/loadingoverlay.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js/application.js"></script>
</body>
</html>